## âœ¨ Features

- **ðŸ“ˆ Descriptive Statistics** â€” Instant stats (mean, std, quantiles) per column
- **ðŸ“Š Correlation Matrix** â€” Heatmaps for Pearson/Spearman correlations
- **ðŸ“‰ Distribution Analysis** â€” Histograms, KDEs, boxplots by column
- **ðŸ§¼ Missing Data Detection** â€” Visual analysis (MCAR, MAR, NMAR)
- **ðŸ› ï¸ Data Cleaning** â€” Forward/backward fill, interpolation, median, mode, etc.
- **ðŸ” Data Transformation** â€” Normalize, standardize, cast, and rename columns
- **ðŸ“‚ CSV Uploads** â€” Drag and drop from your browser
- **ðŸ§ª Jupyter Notebook Integration** â€” Launch with `bvista.show(df)`
- **ðŸ“¡ Real-time Sync** â€” WebSocket-powered updates between sessions
- **ðŸŒ Web-based UI** â€” Modern interface powered by React + Vite

> ðŸ” [See full feature breakdown â†’](docs/features.md)

