## ðŸ“ˆ Usage Examples

### 1. Notebook + UI

```python
import pandas as pd
import bvista

df = pd.read_csv("data.csv")
bvista.show(df)
```

### 2. API Upload

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:5050/api/upload \
     -F 'file=@your_file.csv'
```

### 3. Trigger WebSocket

```python
socketio.emit("data_update", {"status": "DataFrame updated"})
```

> Full API listed [here](docs/usage/api_endpoints.md)

